    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In Dei nomine. Anno dominice nativitatis millesimo centesimo octuagesimo
                        VIIII, tempore <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/4316"
                            >C[l]ementis</persName> pape et <persName>Frederici</persName>
                        imperatoris, die XI intrante mensis februarii, indictione VII, <placeName
                            ref="#places/80">Ferrarie</placeName>, in domo Comunis. Nos <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Aegidius Blasii">Egidius
                            Blasii</name></persName> et <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Wido de Villanova">Guido de Villanova</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudices</rs> Comunis Ferrarie cognitores controversie que
                        vertitur inter <persName><name ref="Petrusbonus">Petrumbonum
                                Sali[ce]tem</name></persName> inpresscia et <persName><name
                                ref="Gregorius">Gregorium</name></persName> ex una parte et
                            <persName key="#Missus"><name ref="Roseus Pomposianus"
                            >Roseum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Missus">procuratorem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Placitum/iudicatum #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Rivers #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Wine #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus #Missus #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName ref="#places/4179"
                                >Ponposie</placeName></orgName> ex altera de <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Casalia">casalibus</rs> et <rs key="#Rivers">aquis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs> positis in <placeName
                            key="#Placitum/iudicatum #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Rivers #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Wine"
                            ref="#places/3559">Laco Sancto</placeName>, que omnia dicebant sibi
                        pertinere per <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enphyt(eusin)</rs>
                        quam Petrusbonus et Gregorius ostendebant et dicebant <rs
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldionem</rs> abbatis eos de
                        possessione illarum rerum in eos degetisse. E contra Roseus pro abbate sibi
                        licuisse dicebat quia dicebat abbatem habere illius tocius loci districtum
                        et predictum Petrumbonum et Gregorium a <rs key="#Servitium">servitiis</rs>
                        que ei facere debebant a <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">prestatione pensionis</rs>
                        cessasse. Et predictus Roseus pro abbate a Petrobono petebat illum quod ipse
                        Petrusbonus possidet de hereditate <persName><name ref="Petrus Pilus">Petri
                                qui vocabatur Pilus</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Gibertini</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Calvus">Calvi</name></persName> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/3592" key="#Placitum/iudicatum">Cocomario</placeName> et
                        illum quod habet de hereditate <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Leo">Leonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerici</rs> et Calvi et <persName><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alberti</name></persName> germanorum et quod ipse
                        Petrusbonus possidet de hereditate <persName><name ref="Antiochia"
                                >Antiochie</name></persName>, que omnia sunt sita in Cocomario
                        maioreet minore. Visis et auditis rationibus utriusque partis et dictis
                        testium diligenter inspectis et viso etiam instrumento henthyt(eusin) et
                        prestito sacramento a Petrobono et Gregorio quod ipsi bene solverunt
                        pensionem pro illa enphyt(eusin) nuntiis abbatis, quam diu ipsius rei
                        habuerunt poss(essionem), predictum Roseum pro abbate ad restitutionem
                        tertie partis earum rerum que continenter in antiqua henphyt(eusin) quam
                        predictus Petrusbonus et Gregorius ostendebant, Petrobono et Gregorio
                        condempnamus salvo iure generaliter iurisdictionis abbati quod habet.
                        Predictum vero Petrumbonum ad restitutionem earum rerum predictarum quas
                        possidet in Cocomario Roseo pro abbate condempnamus. Ad hec fuerunt testes:
                        Donatus, Rolandus Ildeprandi, domnus Leutius, Iohannes Periculi, Bonus
                        Iohannes, Albertus de Lusia, Iannibellus, Guido de Galeria, Martinus,
                        Rodulfus pelliparius. EGO <persName key="#Notary">
                            <name ref="Berardus">BERARDUS</name></persName> Christi misericordia
                        sacri palatii et tunc Comunis Ferrarie <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        interfui ut audivi et intellexi rogatus scripsi.</ab>
